		<div id="comment_body_64110085"><p>I agree that it's probably not poaching if the target of the poach approached Apple first.</p><p>However, that doesn't mean there still isn't patent infringement going on here, because any work that engineer did on this patent was paid for by Masimo, and Masimo owns the patent even if his name is on it.</p><p>Thus, the "poaching" is circumstantial in nature, and orthogonal to the patent infringement issue.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64110085">

</div>
